316
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:56,716
I now finally understand

317
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:59,380
what he meant by this self-consciousness.

318
00:14:00,700 --> 00:14:01,756
Brother Shou Chang,

319
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:03,156
Two months ago you were clamouring

320
00:14:03,180 --> 00:14:06,236
to criticise Chen Duxiu for his pessimistic and self-conscious approach to the world.

321
00:14:06,260 --> 00:14:07,476
In the blink of an eye,

322
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:09,636
