328
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:21,596
How many people are complaining?

329
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:23,236
But what about now?

330
00:14:23,260 --> 00:14:28,180
Overthrowing Yuan has become the consensus of the whole country.

331
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:29,836
At this point

332
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:30,996
you have to admit

333
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:33,236
that Chen Duxiu had a great vision.

334
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:33,556
Too much.

335
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:34,596
Is that enough?

336
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:36,660
You're killing me.

337
00:14:38,620 --> 00:14:40,020
Yihan.

338
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:43,196
Awakening the minds of the people

339
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:45,436
is also something I have always wanted to do to

340
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:48,260
I can't read this book anymore.

341
00:14:53,820 --> 00:14:55,076
This is a letter from him to me.

342
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:57,596
I hope that our Chinese Students Association

343
00:14:57,620 --> 00:15:00,300
will contribute to the "Youth Magazine" in large numbers.

