with the same common purpose of serving the country.

379
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:51,196
How grand.

380
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:52,156
You all

381
00:17:52,157 --> 00:17:52,156
seem to be making a pact of brotherhood.

382
00:17:52,180 --> 00:17:55,420
{\an8}[Ge Jianhao, mother of Cai Heseen]

