00:18:02,260 --> 00:18:03,380
You know, Runzhi.

387
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:04,876
Oh, Runzhi.

388
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:07,620
That kid is something!

389
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:10,956
