392
00:18:11,980 --> 00:18:15,076
Which one of you is '28 Strokes Student'?

393
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:16,076
Hello, hello.

394
00:18:16,100 --> 00:18:17,796
I am here to apply for the meeting of friends.

395
00:18:17,820 --> 00:18:19,156
My name is Cai Hesen.

396
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:19,876
How do you do?

397
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:22,036
This is Xiao Zisheng.

398
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:23,116
How do you do?

399
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:25,236
My hands are covered with ink.

400
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,196
Chen Chang.

401
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:26,636
Hello.

402
00:18:26,660 --> 00:18:28,636
This one, this is He Shuheng.

403
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:30,036
How do you do.

404
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:32,276
And '28 Strokes Student' is...

405
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:33,876
He'll be right back.

406
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:35,436
Eat first.

407
00:18:35,460 --> 00:18:36,740
Ok.

408
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:49,740
I've found a treasure! I've found a treasure!

409
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:50,876
28 Strokes Student is back.

410
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:51,476
Mother Ge.

411
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:52,956
You've worked hard.

412
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:54,076
Runzhi,

413
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:56,236
What are you talking about?

414
00:18:56,260 --> 00:18:57,276
"Sent to the foothills"

415
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,396
"Hidden in the famous mountains"

416
00:18:58,420 --> 00:18:59,276
Ah, right.

417
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:00,276
From "The Book of Documents"

418
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:01,396
"Sent to the foothills"

419
00:19:01,420 --> 00:19:03,756
"Though he is late because of thunder and rain, he is not lost."

420
00:19:03,780 --> 00:19:04,916
28 Strokes Student,

421
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:05,556
I believe,

422
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:07,876
the Heavens is about to confer a great responsibility.

423
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:10,340
Runzhi, a new friend.

424
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:13,636
"Whoever rescues the nation"

425
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:15,636
"Is considered a kindred spirit."

426
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:16,596
New friend,

427
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:17,756
what is your name?

428
00:19:17,780 --> 00:19:18,556
You are too kind.

429
00:19:18,580 --> 00:19:19,476
You are too kind.

430
00:19:19,477 --> 00:19:20,476
My name is Li Lisan.

431
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:20,516
{\an8}[Li Lisan, student at Hunan Guangyi School]

432
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:22,276
I come from Liling, Hunan.

433
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:23,636
I am '28 Strokes Student'

434
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:24,556
Mao Zedong.

435
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:26,820
Hello. How do you do.

436
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:28,756
Please sit.

437
00:19:28,780 --> 00:19:29,916
Take a look at my treasure.

438
00:19:29,940 --> 00:19:30,596
Sure.

439
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:32,116
What treasure?

440
00:19:32,140 --> 00:19:33,196
Come, come, come.

441
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,436
Lend a hand.

442
00:19:34,460 --> 00:19:35,196
Runzhi,

443
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:35,636
To the side.

444
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:36,996
Lost your manners?

445
00:19:37,020 --> 00:19:39,316
You'll know it when you see it.

446
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:41,060
Here.

447
00:19:41,460 --> 00:19:42,596
Look.

448
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:44,820
This is my treasure.

449
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:45,956
One for each.

450
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:48,820
One book a person.

451
00:19:49,540 --> 00:19:50,116
Today,

452
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:51,356
at our recruitment meeting,

453
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,196
let's discuss this,

454
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,396
and nothing else.

455
00:19:53,420 --> 00:19:54,996
Come, take a look.

456
00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:56,516
Look at this first,

457
00:19:56,540 --> 00:19:57,476
Look, look.

458
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:58,956
This really is a treasure.

459
00:19:58,980 --> 00:19:59,836
Everyone,

460
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:02,476
This is Mr. Chen Duxiu's "The Youth Magazine."

461
00:20:02,500 --> 00:20:03,636
Mr. Yang Changji

462
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:05,316
has already recommended it to us many times.

463
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:07,836
He says it is the prescription to save the nation.

464
00:20:07,860 --> 00:20:09,276
Run Huan is right.

465
00:20:09,300 --> 00:20:11,956
This is the remedy that will save lives.

466
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:12,676
I've only

467
00:20:12,700 --> 00:20:15,156
briefly skimmed the founding statement.

468
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:15,996
Reading

469
00:20:16,020 --> 00:20:17,236
"A Call to the Youth"

470
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:18,276
I felt as if

471
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:20,716
I've been struck by a thunderbolt.

472
00:20:20,740 --> 00:20:22,180
Absolutely enlightening!

473
00:20:22,420 --> 00:20:23,396
Runzhi,

474
00:20:23,420 --> 00:20:25,756
You've bought so many issues at once.

475
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:28,060
How are you going to eat this month?

476
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:30,756
'Tis enough to have this book.

477
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:31,756
Runzhi,

478
00:20:31,780 --> 00:20:33,316
don't worry and read your book.

479
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:34,636
If you do get hungry

480
00:20:34,660 --> 00:20:35,876
come to Mother Ge

481
00:20:35,900 --> 00:20:36,636
and you'll definitely

482
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:38,676
eat your fill.

483
00:20:38,700 --> 00:20:40,196
Here. Great.

484
00:20:40,220 --> 00:20:42,260
I'm actually hungry.

485
00:20:45,500 --> 00:20:47,236
You've reminded me.

486
00:20:47,260 --> 00:20:48,556
Mother Ge,

487
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:50,076
remember to make it spicy.

488
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:51,596
The very spicy kind.

489
00:20:51,620 --> 00:20:52,836
Got it for you.

490
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,396
Thank you!

491
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:55,076
Everyone,

492
00:20:55,100 --> 00:20:57,156
I'm so energized.

493
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,316
Haven't we always been talking

494
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:00,036
about creating a new people?

495
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:01,516
Well, what is the new youth?

496
00:21:01,540 --> 00:21:02,556
Mr. Chen Zhongfu

497
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:03,396
right here

498
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:05,660
talks about six criteria.

499
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:08,036
Be independent, and not servile.

500
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:10,516
Be progressive, and not conservative.

501
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:13,276
Be aggressive, and not retiring.

502
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:15,436
Be cosmopolitan, and not isolationist.

503
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:18,036
Be utilitarian, and not formalistic.

504
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:20,276
Be scientific, and not fanciful.

505
00:21:20,300 --> 00:21:21,516
Wonderfully put!

506
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:23,636
The six criteria proposed by Mr. Zhongfu

507
00:21:23,660 --> 00:21:24,956
is exactly the direction to work towards

508
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:25,996
for my generation.

509
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:26,796
True.

510
00:21:26,820 --> 00:21:28,196
These six criteria are good,

511
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:29,196
but I don't think

512
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:31,100
they are comprehensive enough.

513
00:21:31,220 --> 00:21:33,260
What do you mean?

514
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:34,276
I just feel

515
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:36,076
there needs to be at least one more.

516
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:38,876
Be sturdy, and not frail.

517
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:40,940
Tell me more.

518
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:47,396
Everyone,

519
00:21:47,420 --> 00:21:48,876
our nation's scholars are more often

520
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:49,916
bookish and frail.

521
00:21:49,940 --> 00:21:51,356
A military spirit has not been encouraged.

522
00:21:51,380 --> 00:21:53,276
Only when the young people boldly striving to save the country

523
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:54,356
are physically strong,

524
00:21:54,380 --> 00:21:56,076
can their efforts be similarily vigorous.

525
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:57,316
Then the moniker bestowed on us by foreigners

526
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:58,836
"the sick man of Asia"

527
00:21:58,860 --> 00:22:00,036
can be actually thrown off completely.

528
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:01,236
Well said. Makes sense.

529
00:22:01,260 --> 00:22:02,076
I approve.

530
00:22:02,100 --> 00:22:03,716
I approve as well.

531
00:22:03,740 --> 00:22:06,060
Yes, I also agree.

532
00:22:26,100 --> 00:22:26,876
You're getting soaked!

533
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:27,916
Don't worry.

534
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:29,620
He's just like this.

535
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:37,716
Civilize the mind,

536
00:22:37,740 --> 00:22:39,276
make savage the body.

537
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:41,476
With both strength of body and strength of convictions

538
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:44,340
There's nothing on earth that's impossible.

539
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,436
Everyone,

540
00:22:47,460 --> 00:22:48,156
This is

541
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:50,236
the new youth of China.

542
00:22:50,260 --> 00:22:51,236
I've thought about it.

543
00:22:51,260 --> 00:22:53,276
I am going to contribute to "Youth Magazine"

544
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:54,396
and discuss in depth

545
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:57,140
the physical education of Chinese people.

546
00:22:57,780 --> 00:23:00,460
Good, good.

547
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:05,316
Like many young students

548
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:08,596
who struggled to find the truest way to save the country,

549
00:23:08,620 --> 00:23:12,940
Moa Zedong's eyes were opened by the magazine "New Youth."

550
00:23:13,060 --> 00:23:14,116
He started to explore

551
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:17,996
the ideas of the early New Culture Movement.

552
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:19,476
During this period,

553
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:22,420
he wrote these words in his diary:

554
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:25,796
In struggling with the sky, is there boundless joy.

555
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:29,396
In struggling with the earth, is there boundless joy.

