00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:04,636
Mr. Chen Duxiu has shared two prescriptions with the public.

600
00:25:04,660 --> 00:25:07,076
Mr. Democracy and Mr. Science

601
00:25:07,100 --> 00:25:09,436
has already come to China.

602
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:12,116
King of steel, Carnegie.

603
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:13,756
That's Carnegie, not Shmarnegie.

604
00:25:13,780 --> 00:25:16,036
Wonderful! Wonderful!

605
00:25:16,060 --> 00:25:20,596
Turns out he was originally just a working boy.

606
00:25:20,620 --> 00:25:23,260
Great!

607
00:25:25,380 --> 00:25:26,636
Hello, excuse me.

608
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:28,076
Take a look, take a peek.

609
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:29,676
"Youth Magazine"

610
00:25:29,700 --> 00:25:32,276
Mr. Democracy and Mr. Science are here.

611
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:35,316
See how Carnegie fulfilled the American Dream.

612
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:38,036
How he went from a worker to the king of steel!

613
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:40,396
Here, take a look.

614
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:47,676
"Youth Magazine" Come, take a look.
Newest edition.

615
00:25:47,700 --> 00:25:48,956
Take a look.

616
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:50,436
Together?

617
00:25:50,460 --> 00:25:52,196
Thank you, thank you.

618
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:54,020
"Youth Magazine"

619
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:55,716
He's from my hometown.

620
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:57,236
His name is Hu Shi.

621
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,916
When he was nineteen years old

622
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,236
he went to study abroad in the US,

623
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:03,156
first at Cornell University to study agricultural science,

624
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:05,716
then he switched his major to literature.

625
00:26:05,740 --> 00:26:08,956
He went to Columbia University this year

626
00:26:08,980 --> 00:26:11,436
to study with that well-known professor, John Dewey,

627
00:26:11,460 --> 00:26:13,796
for a doctorate of philosophy.

628
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,276
It can be said that this child

629
00:26:15,300 --> 00:26:17,316
is proficient in literature, history, and philosophy.

630
00:26:17,317 --> 00:26:18,916
He saw an issue of our "Youth Magazine"

631
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:19,916
{\an8}[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Cun, New Culture Movement activist]

632
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:21,036
and was very excited.

633
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:22,460
He's sent a letter

634
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:25,636
and wants to write an article regarding the revolution in literature.

635
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:29,460
So I would like to solicit your opinions.

636
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:34,620
That's great!

637
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:39,020
This topic of literary revolution is great.

638
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:40,516
I really didn't expect

639
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:42,716
a student who has been overseas for years

640
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:46,076
to be capable of seeing the purpose of my magazine

641
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,636
so incisively.

642
00:26:47,660 --> 00:26:49,620
Genius!

643
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:51,836
A kindred spirit!

644
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:52,396
Alright, Zhong Fu

645
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:53,436
A sworn friend!

646
00:26:53,460 --> 00:26:54,676
That's enough.

647
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:57,076
Zhong Fu, a young man's letter

648
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:58,476
can get you so excited?

649
00:26:58,500 --> 00:26:59,516
Aren't you too ridiculous?

650
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:00,780
Not by half!

651
00:27:00,780 --> 00:27:03,140
Ideological guidance cannot be idle chit-chat,

652
00:27:03,140 --> 00:27:04,556
but start from a concrete basis

653
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:06,196
that focuses on the lives of the masses.

654
00:27:06,220 --> 00:27:07,956
"Literary Revolution: A Tentative Proposal"

655
00:27:07,980 --> 00:27:10,396
If this article is written properly,

656
00:27:10,420 --> 00:27:11,996
it will be a bombshell!

657
00:27:12,020 --> 00:27:14,116
Bai Sha, the younger generation will in time surpass us!

658
00:27:14,140 --> 00:27:14,756
This Hu Shi

659
00:27:14,780 --> 00:27:16,596
is too important for our "Youth Magazine."

660
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,596
Must grab him!

661
00:27:17,620 --> 00:27:19,580
Oh Zhong Fu,

662
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:21,036
in this time and age,

663
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:24,796
it's not easy to find a genius

664
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:27,236
who can catch your eye.

665
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:29,036
Though don't get too hung up on it.

666
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:31,756
This guy is a doctoral student in the United States,

667
00:27:31,780 --> 00:27:33,596
and a disciple of Professor Dewey.

668
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:35,636
As if you can grab him just by saying so.

669
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:36,876
This guy lives in the United States.

670
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:38,476
Whether he can even come back is an issue.

671
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:40,076
No, no. This I can guarantee.

672
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:42,676
He will definitely return to China after completing his studies.

673
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:44,980
How can one be sure?

674
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:47,516
This guy, Hu Shi,

675
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:49,356
is a filial son.

676
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:51,036
Before he went abroad to study,

677
00:27:51,060 --> 00:27:54,036
his mother arranged a marriage for him.

678
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:56,196
His mother can't wait to get a grandson.

679
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:58,836
So she writes him letters every few days

680
00:27:58,860 --> 00:28:01,716
telling him to come back after he finishes his studies to get married.

681
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:03,356
He would not dare to disobey his mother.

682
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:05,436
This person is really too wonderful.

683
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,876
His thinking is wonderful.

684
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:07,156
What?

685
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:08,856
Grab him!

686
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:11,580
Grab him as soon as he comes back.

687
00:28:26,300 --> 00:28:27,796
Junman!

688
00:28:27,820 --> 00:28:29,860
Here, let me.

689
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:36,076
Why is your cough so bad?

690
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:37,276
You took your medicine?

691
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:38,660
I did. It's not effective.

692
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:40,916
It's not effective?

693
00:28:40,940 --> 00:28:42,076
You have to keep taking it.

694
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:44,156
How can the medicine work if you don't keep taking it?

695
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:45,356
I've finished it.

696
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:47,636
But there were no results.

697
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:49,860
You've finished it.

698
00:28:50,820 --> 00:28:51,996
Ok, alright.

699
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:53,396
Don't work any more.

700
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:55,436
Go rest in the house.

701
00:28:55,460 --> 00:28:56,676
Let me sit here for a bit.

702
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:58,340
Get some air.

703
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:03,700
Then wait. I will go buy medicine.

704
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,756
You don't need to go.

705
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:06,956
The drawer has long run out of money.

706
00:29:06,980 --> 00:29:08,796
The money you gave me last month is all used up.

707
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:10,516
It's an old problem.

708
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:11,676
It'll pass.

709
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:14,340
Don't worry. I'm not dying.

710
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:16,076
Gao Junman!

711
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:17,356
Don't work anymore!

712
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:19,396
No one's dying if the firewood's not chopped.

713
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:21,300
Go inside and rest.

714
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:23,140
Wait for me.

715
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:28,916
No one's dying if the firewood's not chopped.

716
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:31,660
Can't cook if the firewood's not chopped!

717
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:46,236
Zhong Fu,

718
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:48,316
why are you here in such a heavy rain?

719
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:49,916
Just dropping by.

720
00:29:49,940 --> 00:29:52,220
Pour your own tea if you want.

721
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:57,140
Those the accounts?

722
00:30:01,260 --> 00:30:03,076
So today,

723
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:05,516
I ran around to collect the money.

724
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:08,596
To date, our "Youth Magazine"

725
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:12,276
has sold 2000 copies in total,

726
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,876
breaking even.

727
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:16,540
The principal has basically been recouped.

728
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:20,580
That's great.

729
00:30:21,900 --> 00:30:24,620
That's a good thing, right?

730
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:28,860
Mengzou,

731
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:30,316
My uh...

732
00:30:30,340 --> 00:30:32,036
This issue's payment for uh,

733
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:33,556
for my editorial.

734
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:36,196
Is that included in the capital?

735
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:37,636
I'm calculating the big accounts.

736
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:40,356
Haven't had a chance yet to take you into consideration.

737
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:42,516
Hold on, you have to take me into consideration as well.

738
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,236
If your capital has been recouped

739
00:30:44,260 --> 00:30:45,916
then shouldn't the payment for my editorial

740
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:49,460
be given back to me?

741
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:54,636
Alright, then let me take you into consideration right now.

742
00:30:54,660 --> 00:30:56,980
Let me see,

743
00:30:57,020 --> 00:31:00,836
Your manuscript fee, editorial fee

744
00:31:00,860 --> 00:31:02,756
added together

745
00:31:02,780 --> 00:31:05,676
is 138 silver dollars.

746
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:08,396
However, you've asked three times for an advance.

747
00:31:08,420 --> 00:31:10,356
The first time, for 4 silver dollars.

748
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:12,236
The second time, also for 4 silver dollars.

749
00:31:12,260 --> 00:31:14,396
The third time, for 10 silver dollars.

750
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:16,036
18 all together.

751
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:18,276
138 minus 18

752
00:31:18,300 --> 00:31:19,116
So you should get

753
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:22,876
120 silver dollars, correct?

754
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:25,420
I'll give it to you right now.

755
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:30,380
Fifty.

756
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:33,380
One hundred.

757
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:35,316
One twenty.

758
00:31:35,340 --> 00:31:36,676
Take it.

759
00:31:36,700 --> 00:31:38,556
I borrowed money three times.

760
00:31:38,580 --> 00:31:41,436
Two $4 and one $10.

761
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:42,916
Why don't I have any impression of this?

762
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:44,996
These matters, you don't need to think over it.

763
00:31:45,020 --> 00:31:46,396
These are the matters I'll look after.

764
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:47,956
As for you, great thinker

765
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:50,116
just unhesitatingly let out your brilliance.

766
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,316
Zhong Fu,

767
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:53,436
you say, this Yuan Shikai,

768
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:56,556
his determination to be the emperor

769
00:31:56,580 --> 00:31:58,636
makes the heavens angry and causes people to resent.

770
00:31:58,660 --> 00:32:01,396
This authority, right now also has no time

771
00:32:01,420 --> 00:32:03,116
to deal with the revolutionaries.

772
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:04,716
As soon as the current political situation starts to ease

773
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:06,036
this business opportunity, it will come.

774
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:08,956
I want to seize onto the opportunity, go out and raise capital.

775
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:11,116
With your great persona, you will have a lot of acquaintances.

776
00:32:11,140 --> 00:32:13,276
Bring over more people with money to invest.

777
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:15,716
This magazine of ours, maybe it will resume operations.

778
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:17,356
Alright. No problem.

779
00:32:17,380 --> 00:32:19,756
You're responsible for finding people, I'll show up personally.

780
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:21,196
As long as the magazine can be managed well,

781
00:32:21,220 --> 00:32:23,116
whatever you have me do is fine.

782
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:25,796
Uncle Wang.

783
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:30,340
You've come back.

784
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:32,940
Dad.

785
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:35,356
Why have you come back so early today?

786
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:37,940
It's raining today, impossible to work.

787
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,636
Mengzou

788
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:43,436
This... Yannian and Qiaonian doing editing here,

789
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:45,276
isn't it that they should have pay too?

790
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:47,676
I gave it to them, Yannian didn't want it.

791
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:49,356
Speaking about this pay,

792
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:52,940
it's made up for in my accommodation fees here.

793
00:32:53,540 --> 00:32:54,876
I want to properly discuss with you,

794
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:56,396
these two children's matters.

795
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:58,636
In the daytime, they are working at the port.

796
00:32:58,660 --> 00:33:00,636
At night, they come over to my place to be editors.

797
00:33:00,660 --> 00:33:02,396
And they still need to learn French.

798
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:04,276
Wouldn't you say these two children are too tired

799
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:08,996
That is to say, the two brothers living costs right now,

800
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:11,916
all depends on the salary from working at the port.

801
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:13,076
That's right.

802
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:15,396
I have also heard, at the port they

803
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:17,236
extended the working time.

804
00:33:17,260 --> 00:33:18,996
I quietly asked Qiaonian

805
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,436
what's going on?

806
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:24,580
He said it's for getting the tuition to learn French.

807
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:27,340
You say, what to do?

808
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:29,476
This child, right now

809
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:31,276
when his body is still growing.

810
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:33,676
If he's like this, wouldn't his body break down?

811
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:36,180
You say, what to do with this?

812
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:39,276
Those two, if they didn't want the editing pay,

813
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:41,156
you should give it me.

814
00:33:41,180 --> 00:33:42,556
I am his father.

815
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:45,156
It should be me... Receiving it...

816
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:47,716
It should be normal too, right?

817
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:49,356
What! This is...

818
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:51,396
That's another matter!

819
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:53,156
Didn't I already tell you?

820
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:55,076
Yannian had the pay

821
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:57,436
included it in the accommodation fees here.

822
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,916
You still say your son and you are very similar,

823
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,556
not even a little similar.

824
00:34:00,580 --> 00:34:02,396
He, give him money and he doesn't want it.

825
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:06,020
You here, keep going on and on with me.

826
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:24,300
This is 50 silver dollars.

